## Troubleshooting

### CSS not updating?

```bash
cd src/Web
Remove-Item wwwroot/css/app.css
npm run build:css
```

### Database locked error (SQLite)?

Stop all running instances:
```bash
Get-Process -Name dotnet | Stop-Process
dotnet run --project src/Web
```

### Migration errors?

Reset migrations:
```bash
# Delete all migration files in Infrastructure/Migrations/
# Delete database file (app.db)
dotnet ef migrations add InitialCreate -p src/Infrastructure -s src/Web
dotnet ef database update -p src/Infrastructure -s src/Web
```

### Port already in use?

Change port in `src/Web/Properties/launchSettings.json`:
```json
{
  "applicationUrl": "http://localhost:5001"
}
```

### HTMX not triggering?

1. Check browser console for errors
2. Verify `HX-Request: true` header in Network tab
3. Check event name spelling in views
4. Use `/_swap/dev/events` dashboard

### Dependency injection errors?

Ensure services are registered in `Web/Extensions/ServiceCollectionExtensions.cs`:

```csharp
services.AddScoped<ITodoRepository, TodoRepository>();
services.AddScoped<ITodoService, TodoService>();
```

