## Git Workflow

### Ignore Generated Files

Already configured in `.gitignore`:
- `bin/`, `obj/` (all projects)
- `src/Web/wwwroot/css/app.css` (generated)
- `src/Web/wwwroot/lib/` (restored via LibMan)
- `node_modules/`
- `*.db` (SQLite files)
- `Migrations/` (can be regenerated)

### Recommended Branches

- `main` — Production-ready code
- `develop` — Integration branch
- `feature/*` — Feature branches

